data.description: This amazing residence is available for sale in the exclusive Bonterra community. The home boasts 4 bedrooms 3.5 bathrooms; this includes 2 masters, one on the first floor and the other upstairs. The Greendale model includes a master bedroom with a full bathroom on the first floor. The kitchen has wooden cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a coffee area. The outdoor area features a patio with a covered terrace. Additionally, there is a spacious laundry area upstairs, a generous loft, and a one-car garage. Amenities include a pool, parks, a game room, a recreational space, a fitness room, and much more. Its prime location offers easy access to Interstate I-75 and the Palmetto Expressway. Sellers are very motivated, bring all offers.
